<mxfile host="Electron" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) draw.io/29.3.0 Chrome/140.0.7339.249 Electron/38.7.2 Safari/537.36" version="29.3.0">
  <diagram name="페이지-1" id="SDnKvEwGEQ2BF1tVjAzU">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1346" dy="1190" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-1" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="멀티플레이어 게임 프로그래밍 문서 정리" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="390" x="20" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-2" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="Actor Replication Flow" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="290" x="40" y="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-3" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="Replication 을 복제로 번역하지만, ai 대답상 동기화에 가깝다고함 정확한건 코드를 봐야 할 것 같음" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="290" x="380" y="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-7" edge="1" parent="1" source="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-4" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-6" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-4" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;strong&gt;복제 중인 모든 Actor를 순회합니다&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot;&gt;AActor::SetReplicates(true)&lt;/code&gt; 상태인 것들)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="290" x="980" y="940" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-6" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=1;" value="얼마나 자주 리플리케이션 될지 결정" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="215" x="1390" y="960" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-8" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="해당 Actor가 초기 휴면 상태(&lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;DORM_Initial&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/code&gt;)인지 확인하고, 그렇다면 즉시 건너뜁니다." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="290" x="980" y="1040" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-9" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot;&gt;NetUpdateFrequency&lt;/code&gt; &lt;/b&gt;값을 확인하여 업데이트가 필요한지 결정합니다. 불필요하면 건너뜁니다." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="290" x="980" y="1140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-10" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot;&gt;AActor::bOnlyRelevantToOwner&lt;/code&gt;가 true이면, &lt;/b&gt;소유 커넥션의 뷰어를 대상으로 &lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot;&gt;AActor::IsRelevancyOwnerFor&lt;/code&gt;를 호출하여 관련성을 확인합니다. 관련이 있으면 해당 커넥션의 소유 관련 목록에 추가합니다. 이 경우 Actor는 단 하나의 커넥션에만 전송됩니다." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="300" x="980" y="1240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-11" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;초기 검사를 통과한 Actor에 대해 &lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot;&gt;AActor::PreReplication&lt;/code&gt;이 호출&lt;/b&gt;됩니다. 이 함수는 특정 커넥션에 프로퍼티를 복제할지 여부를 결정하는 곳입니다. &lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot;&gt;DOREPLIFETIME_ACTIVE_OVERRIDE&lt;/code&gt;를 사용하세요." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="110" width="305" x="985" y="1420" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-12" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;Actor 복제는 Network Driver(Net Driver)가 어떤 Actor를 어떤 커넥션에 어떤 순서로 복제할지 결정하는 상세하고 다단계적인 프로세스입니다. 이 페이지에서는 Actor 복제 프로세스에 대한 개요를 제공합니다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;Actor 복제의 대부분은 &lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot;&gt;U&lt;b&gt;NetDriver::ServerReplicateActors&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt;함수 내부에서 이루어집니다. 이 함수에서 서버는 각 클라이언트에 관련성이 있다고 판단한 모든 Actor를 먼저 수집한 뒤, 마지막으로 각 연결된 클라이언트가 업데이트된 이후 변경된 프로퍼티를 전송합니다. 그런 다음&lt;b&gt; &lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot;&gt;UActorChannel::ReplicateActor&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/b&gt; 함수가 특정 채널로의 Actor 복제 세부 사항을 처리합니다.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="540" x="60" y="270" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-13" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="424" width="757" x="75" y="520" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-14" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="377" width="725" x="75" y="1000" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-15" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="573" width="737" x="69" y="1430" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-16" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="518" width="735" x="71" y="2040" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-17" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="490" width="735" x="75" y="2600" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-18" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="437" width="722" x="75" y="3090" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-19" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="442" width="738" x="75" y="3527" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-20" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="346" width="706" x="75" y="3969" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="47_Y47ZIK-oFz3ixZD5e-21" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;" value="&lt;b&gt;서버의 작동 원리&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. 액터 네트워크 휴면 상태 기능이 있고, 일시정지 및 강제 Tick 기능 등이 있다.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;2.리플리케이트된 엑터는 서버와 클라이언트에 동시에 존재, 플레이어는 클라이언트 컨트롤러에 빙의 되어 사용이 되며, 빙이되면 소유자는 서로 연관성이 있게된다.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;3.&amp;nbsp; Actor 별로 Role 을 지정할 수 있는데 , 서버에서만 실행 하는지 , 클라에서만 작동하는지 등등 지정 가능&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;4. 리플레케이션 서버는 거리기반으로 Relevancy 로 Actor 간의 연관성을 지을 수 있다.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;5. 업데이트 빈도 변경 가능&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="156" width="590" x="950" y="1644" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
